BRIEFLY 
New Offer for De Laurentiis: Roth-Stern Group and a group of associated 
companies plan to present an offer to acquire DeLaurentiis Entertainment Group. 
The offer will be submitted today to DEG and its creditors committee in DEG's 
reorganization under Chapter 11 of the U.S. Bankruptcy Code. The group said it 
intends to buy DEG in order to enhance the buyers' film packaging and financing 
unit, the Stern-Herman organization. The purchase will be made through a newly 
formed company. The purchase price was not disclosed. 
